sentence: how many people live in spokane washington ?
sentence-with-vars: how many people live in city0 state0 ?
sql: select city.population from city where city.city_name = ' spokane ' and city.state_name = ' washington ' ;
sql-with-vars: select city.population from city where city.city_name = ' city0 ' and city.state_name = ' state0 ' ;
